# RENDERS & EXPORTS (LARGE BINARY FILES)
# ============================================================================

# Rendered frames (PNG/JPG sequences) - Can be 100s of MB to GBs
projects/*/renders/*
!projects/*/renders/.gitkeep
!projects/*/renders/README.md

# Video exports - Binary files, 5-50 MB each
projects/*/exports/*.mp4
